&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Roboyo&amp;nbsp;AI&amp;nbsp;is a category shaper in Applied AI and Agentic Automation.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We help leading enterprises move from automation projects and AI experiments into governed, production-grade systems that execute real work across workflows, processes,&amp;nbsp;products&amp;nbsp;and services.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:100,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:252}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Our heritage is in scaled enterprise automation; our future is&amp;nbsp;Applied AI and&amp;nbsp;Agentic&amp;nbsp;Automation: autonomous agents, AI engineering squads, process orchestration, data and knowledge foundations, and human-in-the-loop governance embedded deeply into how our clients&amp;nbsp;operate.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:100,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:252}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We are not here to sell AI theatre. We are here to turn AI into&amp;nbsp;working systems, measurable&amp;nbsp;outcomes&amp;nbsp;and repeatable transformation programs.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:140,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:252}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;scriptor-paragraph&quot;&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The AI Lead is a high-impact, hands-on engineering role responsible for architecting and delivering end-to-end AI and agentic automation solutions for enterprise clients. This role sits at the intersection of technical delivery, system design, and strategic influence. You will build production-grade AI systems powered by LLMs and modern cloud platforms, while acting as a trusted advisor to stakeholders—translating complex requirements into scalable solutions that drive real business value. In addition to delivery, you will mentor engineers, contribute to best practices, and help define how AI and agent-based systems are implemented across products, workflows, and enterprise environments. This is a builder-first role: you are expected to actively code and deliver systems in production. You will also play a key role in helping shape how enterprises adopt AI and agent-based systems at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;KEY RESPONSIBILITIES&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead end-to-end design and delivery of AI modules — from architecture to production deployment — for complex, multi-component features, leveraging GCP and Microsoft AI ecosystem capabilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define LLM integration patterns, RAG strategies, and data pipeline architectures; own technical quality and performance of these systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as the primary technical interface with cross-functional stakeholders; participate in requirements workshops and solution demos.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive design reviews, establish engineering standards, and actively mentor engineers on the team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and address technical debt, reliability risks, and scalability bottlenecks proactively.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;scriptor-paragraph&quot;&gt;Deliver agentic automation solutions across enterprise use cases&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
